# Belt-and-suspenders alongside package.json `files` allowlist. Anything not in `files` is
# already excluded — the entries below are just an extra safety net for anything that a future
# `files` edit might accidentally admit.
test/
scripts/
.github/
plans/
docs/
*.tgz
*.log
.env
.env.*
.npmrc
node_modules/
.git/
.gitattributes
.gitignore
.vscode/
.idea/
coverage/
RELEASE_CHECKLIST.md
skills/flow/plans/
skills/flow/tests/

# Python bytecode — regenerated at runtime, wasteful to ship (~130 KB across .310/.311/.314)
**/__pycache__/**
*.pyc
*.pyo
